Package: violoop-rknn
Version: 2.3.2
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Alex <alexliu@zcdigitalsglobal.com>
Description: Rockchip RKNN Runtime Library
 Prebuilt libraries and headers for Rockchip NPU inference
 platform (rkllm-runtime). Provides the rknn C/C++ API for
 deploying AI models on RK3588/RK3576/RK3562/RV1126B.
